---
<section class="newsletter">
  <p class="nl-kicker reveal">Join the Maison</p>
  <h2 class="nl-headline reveal delay-100">The Private Edit</h2>
  <p class="nl-sub reveal delay-200">New arrivals, lookbook releases, and rare access — before anyone else.</p>
  <form class="nl-form reveal delay-300" onsubmit="handleSubscribe(event)">
    <input
      type="email"
      class="nl-input"
      placeholder="Your email address"
      required
      aria-label="Email address"
    />
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark nl-submit">Subscribe</button>
  </form>
</section>
